This directory is used to store the AI statement and citation of third-party resources.
We hereby somnly declare an oath:
we would credit sources and follow licence rules.
We don't copy other teams' work
We do not use undisclosed third-party or AI-generated work in assessed deliverables
We design inclusively and check accessibility basics
We would honestly and comprehensively cite all resources we use that do not belongs to us in our project
We would honestly and comprehensively make an AI statement which documents everything we make with the aid of AI (Although this cource allows full use of AI)
